      "writtenOn": "2018-05-03T18:05:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Does nc stand for \"new context\"? (I\u0027m pretty slow to adjust to this ultra-short variable name convention in Go...)",
      "revId": "af60ac12d61b409eee25b77f4f60d806d775d02a",
